---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { CONTACT_EMAIL } from '../../lib/constants';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy in accordance with GDPR.">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose mt-10">
      <h2>Controller</h2>
      <p>
        Ing. Michael Linder, MSc<br />
        Strali Solutions e.U.<br />
        Nötsch 219, 9611 Nötsch im Gailtal, Austria<br />
        Email: <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Principle</h2>
      <p>
        This website does not collect, store, or process personal data beyond what is technically necessary. No cookies are set, no tracking is used, and no analytics services are employed.
      </p>

      <h2>Hosting and Cloudflare</h2>
      <p>
        This website is hosted on private infrastructure and served via Cloudflare Tunnel (Cloudflare, Inc., 101 Townsend St, San Francisco, CA 94107, USA). Cloudflare processes technically necessary connection data (IP address, timestamp, requested URL) to ensure availability and protection against attacks. Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest). Cloudflare is certified under the EU-U.S. Data Privacy Framework. Standard Contractual Clauses are in place for international data transfers.
      </p>

      <h2>Server Log Files</h2>
      <p>
        The web server automatically records technical data with each access: IP address, timestamp, requested page, browser identifier. This data serves exclusively to ensure technical operation and is not combined with other data sources. Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR.
      </p>

      <h2>No Cookies, No Tracking</h2>
      <p>
        This website does not set cookies and does not use any tracking or analytics tools. The only client-side storage concerns your colour scheme preference (light/dark) in your browser's localStorage. This information does not leave your browser.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you contact me by email, the data you provide (email address, content) will be stored for the purpose of processing your enquiry. No disclosure to third parties takes place. Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR or Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR.
      </p>

      <h2>External Links</h2>
      <p>
        This website contains links to external websites (e.g. LinkedIn, GitHub, strali.solutions). The respective privacy policies of those websites apply to data processing there.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You have the right to access, rectification, erasure, restriction of processing, data portability, and objection. Requests can be directed to <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>. Complaints may be filed with the Austrian Data Protection Authority (<a href="https://www.dsb.gv.at" target="_blank" rel="noopener">dsb.gv.at</a>).
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
